Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.70,0:15:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come and pick up\Nthe money next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, my batteries are running out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Rika.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I worrying too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Can everybody come here for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked Rika to check up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.93,0:16:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.93,0:16:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamamoto can't make\Ntoday's late afternoon shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Can somebody fill in for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but my child\Ngets home early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Onoda? Onoda?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do it?\NYes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:16:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.26,0:16:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not home yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Kyoko. Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So she started working part-time.\NI think it's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.77,0:16:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to be the one who\Nwears the pants in your household.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.72,0:17:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You just want her to\Nstay home all the time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really want that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.63,0:17:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Yura is beautiful. So maybe\Nshe'll be seduced by another guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!\NThat's what I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. The problem I see\Nis that you're really jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, if Yura worked\Nin a place full of women...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.71,0:17:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...or worked by herself, then you\Nwouldn't have any problems, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But you see,\Ngirls find that to be boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.36,0:17:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yura is an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:17:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.50,0:17:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though she's a housewife.\NThey all are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls want to put on makeup or dress\Nnice to catch other people's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's different from\Nhaving fun or cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.31,0:18:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Working as a waitress\Nis really difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.18,0:18:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Approaching customers\Nand meeting their demands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.98,0:18:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But girls really enjoy\Ndoing things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.95,0:18:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to do cosplay too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I would try it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Makoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I called your cell phone, but there was\Nno answer, so I sent you a text message.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, my phone was turned off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.22,0:19:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't read my text message?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:20:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be lying if I said\NI wasn't worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I was doing some soul-searching.\NI didn't trust you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.74,0:20:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought maybe it was because\NI didn't love you enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Makoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we can't contact each other\Nthrough phones and text messages...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...we can still reach\Neach other's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.99,0:20:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I right, Yura?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry!\NI'll fix your dinner real fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,About 20...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait about 30 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you were going to be late, then\Nyou should've bought some appetizers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.58,0:20:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still new at this, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.25,0:20:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:21:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you peel the onions?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.14,0:21:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.\NThanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! Please don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.28,0:21:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Makoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.49,0:21:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a happy man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Makoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We're doing it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.14,0:22:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Yura.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.84,0:22:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really tight...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.84,0:22:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Makoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.75,0:22:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yura...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.49,0:22:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.38,0:23:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Makoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.71,0:23:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to quit my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.72,0:23:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.78,0:23:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to cook and clean at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.96,0:23:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,When you come home,\NI want you to feel relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.56,0:23:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the kind of place\NI want this to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.10,0:23:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go back to work\Nwhenever you feel like.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.70,0:23:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.66,0:24:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You try to make it look\Nas if nothing is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.40,0:24:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Knife of love won't show any mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.21,0:24:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You just hold back your feelings\Nand live each and everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.82,0:24:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You say you're used to it or\Nthere's nothing you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.53,0:24:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be much\Nmore straightforward...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.87,0:24:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...and hug each other real tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.77,0:24:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we're feeling\Nawkward at times...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.61,0:24:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,On the night when I dream\Nas many times as I shed tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.35,0:25:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...l'm sure an angel will smile at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.09,0:25:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's dream of all the stars in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.80,0:25:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you keep on smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.61,0:25:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's dream of all the stars in the sky.